            <ul class="p">
                <li><strong>Protein-Rich Smoothie:</strong> Blend Greek yogurt, berries, spinach, ground flaxseed, and a small banana. Add a scoop of high-quality protein powder if additional protein is needed.</li>
                <li><strong>Veggie Egg Scramble:</strong> Two eggs scrambled with sautéed bell peppers, spinach, and mushrooms. Serve with a slice of whole-grain toast and avocado.</li>
                <li><strong>Overnight Chia Pudding:</strong> Mix chia seeds with milk (dairy or plant-based), add a touch of honey, vanilla, and top with fresh berries and chopped nuts in the morning.</li>
            </ul>

            <p class="p"><strong>Lunch Options:</strong></p>
